home_body_text1: Welcome to Wa no Miyabi. Our shop is a place where you can experience the traditional beauty of Japan.
home_body_text2: The store offers handmade crafts and accessories that combine contemporary design.
home_body_text3: Each and every item is made with care to add color to your daily life.
home_body_text4: We hope that you will find it useful. Please come and visit us.
